text: Jan Raszka (2 December 1928 - 5 February 2007) was a Polish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2007 deaths Category:Polish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Poland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:People from Wisła
